title: War of the Roses: All Over a Canceled Flight
description: Keisha called in for WOTR today to talk about her new boyfriend, Troy who started acting a bit weird after a trip they got planned had a flight cancel. Things started to get weird after that and Keisha wanted to get to the bottom of it.
